org.propelgraph

Interface RDFHTTPLoadingGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Graph

    public interface RDFHTTPLoadingGraph
extends Graph
    This interface is generally for classes that have methods that are particularly fast at loading RDF from HTTP streams. Particularlly gzip compressed streams of Turtle format.
    Author:
    ccjason (8/19/2014)
    See Also:
    LoadCSV

      • add_turtle_rdf_data_from_http_url

        void add_turtle_rdf_data_from_http_url(String url,
                                     long maxlines)
        populates a graph from a RDF resource at the specified HTTP url. That data should be in turtle or n-triple format. It does not assume the graph is initially empty.
        Parameters:
        url -
        maxlines - number of lines of rdf file to read
